{"data":[{"date":"10:22 16/06","title":"Diego Costa b\u1ee9c x\u00fac khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/diego-costa-buc-xuc-khi-tbn-bi-cam-hoa.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Diego Costa cho r\u1eb1ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn Iberia v\u1eeba qua.</h2><h2>Diego Costa l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, Costa b\u1ee9c x\u00fac h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, Costa b\u1ee9c x\u00fac h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Tay-Ban-Nha-bi-cam-hoa,-Costa-buc-xuc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Costa l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00e3 hai l\u1ea7n gi\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 khi Ronaldo ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Fernando Hierro \u0111\u00e3 trao cho Costa c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay v\u00ec Iago Aspas, Lucas Vazquezhay Rodrigo. V\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf cho Hierro th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e2m mi\u1ec7ng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t sung m\u00e3n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c khi \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Costa kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 ng\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, g\u1eb7p Ma-r\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Kaliningrad v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 4 tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 Diego Costa cho r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ed1t t\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tranh lu\u1eadn. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng may cho Costa l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lu m\u1edd b\u1edfi hat-trick c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. V\u00e0 sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Iran \u0111ang t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng B nh\u1edd chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma-r\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pique-buc-xuc-ronaldo-gioi-an-va-de-kiem-da-phat-421-188609.html\">Pique b\u1ee9c x\u00fac: Ronaldo gi\u1ecfi \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-sieu-kich-tinh-421-188601.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"221","checkdouble":"188614"},{"date":"10:06 16/06","title":"Ronaldo \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n troll \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-an-mung-ban-thang-bang-man-troll-dich-thu-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00eam qua, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ea1y th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u1eb1ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea5y tay vu\u1ed1t c\u1eb1m v\u1edbi d\u1ee5ng \u00fd \"\u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y\" Lionel Messi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huy-diet-tay-ban-nha-ronaldo-lap-them-ky-luc-moi-469-188608.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eeba x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span> sau khi l\u1eadp hat-trick \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Seleccao tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN. CR7 s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo troll Messi khi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u0110N 3-3 TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo troll Messi khi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u0110N 3-3 TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Ronaldo_an_mung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pha \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea7y khi\u00eau kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Messi. \u1ea2nh: Getty Images.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nY\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0103n m\u1eebng sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0a tay l\u00ean c\u1eb1m v\u00e0 chu m\u00f4i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t d\u00e1ng v\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y khi\u00eau kh\u00edch. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia, m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Real Madrid nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ec3 \"\u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y\" ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Lionel Messi, \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 truy\u1ec1n ki\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a anh su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ed9t h\u00e3ng s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1ec3 thao ch\u1ea1y chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina v\u1edbi slogan: \"Leo Messi: The G.O.A.T\". Trong \u0111\u00f3, \"G.O.A.T\" l\u00e0 vi\u1ebft t\u1eaft c\u1ee7a c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb ti\u1ebfng Anh \"Greatest Of All Time\" (t\u1ea1m d\u1ecbch: hay nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i).\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buc anh Messi dang be mot chu de nam trong chien dich quang cao\" title=\"B\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh Messi \u0111ang b\u1ebf m\u1ed9t ch\u00fa d\u00ea n\u1eb1m trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Messi_quang_cao_1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh Messi \u0111ang b\u1ebf m\u1ed9t ch\u00fa d\u00ea n\u1eb1m trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \"Leo Messi: The G.O.A.T\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong ti\u1ebfng Anh, \"goat\" c\u00f2n c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 con d\u00ea. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Ronaldo d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng gi\u1ea3 con v\u1eadt n\u00e0y trong pha \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u1eb1m g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch: T\u00f4i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 G.O.A.T ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi, li\u1ec7u Messi c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi? 20h t\u1ed1i nay 16/6, Messi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Iceland, \"ng\u1ef1a \u00f4\" t\u1ea1i EURO 2016 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>.<br>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"220","checkdouble":"188615"},{"date":"10:28 16/06","title":"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 16/6","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/lich-truyen-hinh-truc-tiep-world-cup-2018-hom-nay-166.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang b\u00e1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 16/6 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i VTV v\u00e0 HTV v\u00e0 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng internet</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 166 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 166 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/lich-truyen-hinh-truc-tiep-world-cup-2018-hom-nay-16-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo g\u1ecdi Messi li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\nLo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n v\u1edbi 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i nay v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai thu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3ng C v\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng D. \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u1eeb Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 Australia. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n theo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Australia c\u1ee7a bongda24h \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng 3-0.  <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D Argentina s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0110T Iceland t\u1eebng g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i Euro 2016. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D Croatia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh Nigeria<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich truyen hinh truc tiep World Cup 2018 dem nay 16/6\" title=\"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay 16/6\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/lich-truyen-hinh-truc-tiep-world-cup-2018-dem-nay-16-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>+ <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-australia-17h00-ngay-166-dau-xuoi-duoi-lot-421-188596.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Australia b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Australia b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div>+ <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-argentina-vs-iceland-20h00-ngay-166-giai-ma-hien-tuong-421-188591.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div>+ <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-peru-vs-dan-mach-23h-ngay-166-khac-biet-o-eriksen-462-188607.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div>+ <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-nigeria-02h00-ngay-176-ban-ha-dai-bang-421-188592.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"219","checkdouble":"188616"},{"date":"10:59 16/06","title":"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ba b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng Sochi, Cristiano Ronaldo thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp c\u00fa hat-trick th\u1ee9 51, trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed 88 n\u0103m c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p 16 n\u0103m qu\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f9i \u00e1o s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadt tr\u1edb tr\u00eau, ch\u01b0a n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng sau khi khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u0103m th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, gi\u1edd th\u00ec Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp mang \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i \u0111au cho ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">48 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/tbn-mat-dau-truoc-world-cup-2018-tia-sang-hy-vong-nao-le-loi-giua-chon-hon-mang-loan-lac-421-188570.html\" target=\"_blank\">La Roja &ldquo;m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7u&rdquo; ngay th\u1ec1m khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018</span> v\u1edbi tr\u00e1t sa th\u1ea3i s\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u00e0nh cho Julen Lopetegui, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00ecn gi\u1eef th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam minh trong l\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 sau khi HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 ngang nhi\u00ean \u0111i \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB tr\u1ef1c thu\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Ronaldo-o-tran-Bo-Dao-Nha-3-3-Tay-Ban-Nha-Hat-trick-ruc-ro!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hat-trick r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Bernabeu v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua &ldquo;gi\u00fap&rdquo; Real Madrid ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c bao ph\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111en l\u00ean chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1ed1n r\u1ea5t chi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai ph\u00fat v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n n\u1eefa th\u00f4i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ng\u1ee1 r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng, l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ngay trong th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc r\u1ed1i ren, lo\u1ea1n l\u1ea1c. Nacho c\u0169ng v\u1eady, v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n &ldquo;t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng&rdquo; n\u00e0o ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n d\u00e0nh cho anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00fat 4, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i&hellip; kh\u00f4ng, anh ng\u00e2y th\u01a1 b\u1ecb Ronaldo qua m\u1eb7t trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, chi\u1ebfu theo n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi tinh qu\u00e1i, &ldquo;\u0111\u1ec3u&rdquo; c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea5p CLB sau khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m penalty.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00fat 58, ch\u00ednh anh v\u1edbi c\u00fa vu\u1ed1t b\u00f3ng m\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i s\u1ea5m s\u00e9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-2 v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec \u01b0u th\u1ebf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 trong n\u1eeda gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 ti\u1ebfp theo, cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p CR7 l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi c\u00fa hat-trick th\u1ee9 51, trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed 88 n\u0103m c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p 16 n\u0103m qu\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f9i \u00e1o s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Bo-Dao-Nha-3-3-Tay-Ban-Nha-Chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh,-Cristiano-Ronaldo!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hat-trick r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0? Ronaldo ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i Ronaldo, m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u00edch k\u1ef7 v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00e1u b\u1eb3n v\u00e0 b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c khi m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n? Th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng b\u1ecf ngo\u00e0i tai. \u0110\u00eam Sochi \u0111\u00e3 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho ni\u1ec1m tin \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00f2n m\u1ecfi c\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 mang vinh quang v\u1ec1 cho T\u1ed5 qu\u1ed1c. Sau khi s\u1edbm chia tay tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Euro 2016 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n cho anh n\u1ebfu l\u1ee7i th\u1ee7i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft t\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfi l\u0103n d\u00e0i tr\u00ean m\u00e1 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m c\u00e1i \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ai c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho anh. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u si\u00eau sao Man Utd thay \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Fernando Santos l\u00e0m lu\u00f4n HLV ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, th\u1ed1ng l\u0129nh khu v\u1ef1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi anh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Bo-Dao-Nha-3-3-Tay-Ban-Nha-Chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh,-Cristiano-Ronaldo!-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hat-trick r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1eeb Paris \u0111\u1ebfn Sochi, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n Ronaldo n\u1ebfu anh bu\u00f4ng b\u1ecf sau tuy\u1ec7t ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Nacho, hay sau khi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng &ndash; m\u1ed9t penalty v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e0 bi\u1ebfu t\u1eeb David De Gea &ndash; \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a b\u1edfi c\u00f4ng lao t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Diego Costa. N\u00f3i th\u1eb3ng ra, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n mang ngh\u0129a l\u00fd g\u00ec s\u1ea5t n\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1eabn mang trong m\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng mi\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Ronaldo bi\u1ebfn t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn th\u00e0nh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t Ronaldo d\u1ed7i h\u1eddn, c\u00e1u b\u1eb3n hay v\u00f9ng v\u1eb1ng trong b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi CR7 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd thu\u1eadn theo t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-sieu-kich-tinh-421-188601.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/diem-nhan-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-sieu-kich-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-sieu-kich-tinh-421-188601.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span><br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean Ronaldo v\u00e0 De Gea. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn derby b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea3n l\u0129nh gi\u00fap anh m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m ng\u00fat ng\u00e0n \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh g\u00ec ph\u00fat 90 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 \u00edt gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4i, anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3ng ph\u1ea1t 18,8 tri\u1ec7u Euro k\u00e8m hai n\u0103m t\u00f9 treo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadn hi\u1ebfn v\u00ec T\u1ed5 qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn v\u1eb9n nguy\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat suy chuy\u1ec3n hay sao nh\u00e3ng, v\u00e0 th\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c th\u00f4ng qua sai l\u1ea7m s\u01a1 \u0111\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n hi\u1ebfm hoi c\u1ee7a De Gea, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hat-trick r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i khi m\u1ecdi hy v\u1ecdng t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea1n ki\u1ec7t, khi m\u1ecdi trang nh\u1ea5t m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 vua Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 n\u00e1t b\u01b0\u01a1m t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong, Ronaldo m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fd mu\u00f4n thu\u1edf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i ph\u00ed ph\u1ea1m m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh ngon \u0103n nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi khi? Ronaldo s\u1ebd s\u00fat tr\u00fang h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o? Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t ghi b\u00e0n n\u1eefa? Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00f4m nay, v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ecbch s\u1eed trong c\u00e1i ch\u00f4n ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a De Gea c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ebft l\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft&hellip;. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo; &ndash; Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sergio Ramos tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-463-188575.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span>&nbsp;k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Ronaldo. Anh \u0111\u00e3 sai, qu\u00e1 sai v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u1ea1nh b\u00ean \u1edf Real Madrid r\u1ed3i!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so Bo Dao Nha 3-3 Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Thong-so-BDN.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha-421-188598.html\">Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huy-diet-tay-ban-nha-ronaldo-lap-them-ky-luc-moi-469-188608.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Ronaldo l\u1eadp h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-an-mung-ban-thang-bang-man-troll-dich-thu-messi-421-188615.html\">Ronaldo \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n troll \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/lap-hattrick-ronaldo-duoc-dong-doi-ca-ngoi-het-loi-469-188611.html\">Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi sau c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot-421-188600.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Ronaldo nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00e0n B\u00f2 t\u00f3t</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"218","checkdouble":"188617"},{"date":"10:47 16/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 16/6: L\u1eadp hattrick, Ronaldo tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/16/tin-nong-world-cup-2018-ngay-166-lap-hattrick-ronaldo-tren-dinh-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (16/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1eadp hattrick, Ronaldo tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">V\u1edbi hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi De Gea, Ronaldo x\u1ebfp ngang h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Pele, Klose v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n trong 4 m\u00f9a World Cup, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi CR7 c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 ph\u00e1 \"k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c\" c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 166 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 166 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Ronaldo-o-tran-Bo-Dao-Nha-3-3-Tay-Ban-Nha-Hat-trick-ruc-ro!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHat-trick c\u1ee7a Ronaldo gi\u00fap anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ea7y vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 4 ghi b\u00e0n trong 4 m\u00f9a World Cup tham d\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Pele v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Uwe Seeler c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 1958, 1962, 1966 v\u00e0 1970. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n trong su\u1ed1t 4 m\u00f9a l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 World Cup Miroslav Klose (2002, 2006, 2010 v\u00e0 n\u0103m 2014).</div>\r\n<h2>Gerard Pique: 'Ronaldo hay \u0103n v\u1ea1 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t'</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique c\u1ee7a Barcelona nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0: \"T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n, c\u00f2n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u00ec c\u00f3 3 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ghi 3 b\u00e0n\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Ph\u1ea3i v\u1ef1c d\u1eady trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup khi ch\u1ecbu m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra\", Pique chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 3 c\u1ee7a \"La Roja\" c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Ronaldo ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn: \"Cristiano r\u1ea5t hay \u0103n v\u1ea1\". B\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha - qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n 11 m - xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ng\u00e3 r\u1ea5t k\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. <br>\r\n<em>Tin b\u00e0i chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pique-buc-xuc-ronaldo-gioi-an-va-de-kiem-da-phat-421-188609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/pique-buc-xuc-ronaldo-gioi-an-va-de-kiem-da-phat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pique-buc-xuc-ronaldo-gioi-an-va-de-kiem-da-phat-421-188609.html\">Pique b\u1ee9c x\u00fac: Ronaldo gi\u1ecfi \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t</span><br>\r\n<span>Trung v\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ee9c x\u00fac sau khi Cristiano Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick, gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>M\u00e8o \u201cti\u00ean tri\u201d Achilles d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 100%</h2>\r\n<div>Sau khi \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00fang k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Nga - \u1ea2 R\u1eadp, ch\u00fa m\u00e8o khi\u1ebfm th\u00ednh Achilles ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y s\u1ed1t khi ch\u1ecdn Iran th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Maroc. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u00e9p s\u00e2n trong su\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Bouhaddouz \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u201cs\u01b0 t\u1eed\u201d ch\u00e2u Phi \u00f4m h\u1eadn. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, m\u00e8o Achilles v\u1eabn \u0111ang xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u00fang 100% k\u00e8o World Cup 2018.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thanh-meo-achilles-lai-du-doan-chinh-xac-ket-qua-world-cup-2018-421-188602.html\">Th\u00e1nh m\u00e8o Achilles l\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1eb7t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u1edf Nga khi\u1ebfn HLV Joachim Low lo l\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div>C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh \u1edf v\u00f9ng ngo\u1ea1i \u00f4 th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Moscow l\u00e0 Vatutinki v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a CLB CSKA Moscow. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Joachim Low \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. \"\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng ng\u1ecdn c\u1ecf t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y qu\u00e1 d\u00e0i. T\u00f4i mong r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c ngay ng\u00e0y mai\".</div>\r\n<h2>Griezmann s\u1ebd nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n n\u1eefa</h2>\r\n<div>HLV \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, Didier Deschamps kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f2n nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u201cL\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e2m l\u00fd khi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Griezmann t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Khi g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd b\u1ecb c\u1edfi b\u1ecf, Griezmann s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Griezmann s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar dung thu ba trong danh sach ghi ban cua DT Brazil.\" title=\"Neymar \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba trong danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/neymar-vi-da-voi-ao-nhu-di-danh-nhau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Neymar t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div>Tr\u00ean k\u00eanh Youtube c\u1ee7a Brazil, Desimpedidos, Neymar t\u1ef1 tin anh ch\u1ec9 thua k\u00e9m Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi: \u201cHai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi. V\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 khi\u00eam nh\u01b0\u1eddng, gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u1edfi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb h\u00e0nh tinh kh\u00e1c\u201d.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"217","checkdouble":"188618"},{"date":"09:11 16/06","title":"Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t 2 n\u0103m t\u00f9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c, khi ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRonaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m, m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1 vi\u00ean s\u1edf thu\u1ebf v\u1ee5 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c Cristiano Ronaldo gian l\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2011-2014, ng\u00f4i sao kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn <strong>14,7 tri\u1ec7u euro</strong>. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo b\u1ecb c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c v\u00ec gian l\u1eadn trong thu nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, khi d\u1ef1ng l\u00ean nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ty ma \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u00f3, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi bu\u1ed9c t\u1ed9i, v\u00e0 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra, thu th\u1eadp b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng. Nh\u01b0ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\" target=\"_blank\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span> di\u1ec5n ra, ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1edd El Mundo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1eadn t\u1ed9i, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u1ed9p l\u1ea1i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n thu\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh th\u00eam chi ph\u00ed h\u1ea7u t\u00f2a, khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p l\u1ea1i <strong>t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 18,8 tri\u1ec7u euro.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn\" title=\"BDN Ronaldo lap cu dup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a h\u1ebft, <strong>CR7 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n t\u00f9 2 n\u0103m. </strong>Th\u00f4ng tin t\u00edch c\u1ef1c duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a ra, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u00e1n n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean vi ph\u1ea1m, Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n t\u00f9 treo. Theo Lu\u1eadt, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 n\u0103m s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p anh b\u1ed3i ho\u00e0n l\u1ea1i chi ph\u00ed.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng thu\u1ebf c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u00ea chu\u1ea9n, nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Lionel Messi c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n t\u00f9 treo 21 th\u00e1ng, do h\u00e0nh vi tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf <strong>4,1 tri\u1ec7u euro.</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a CR7, khi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y anh l\u1eadp hattrick trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, h\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;c\u1ea1nh tr\u1ea1nh&rdquo; v\u1edbi Lionel Messi tr\u00ean &ldquo;m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot-421-188600.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot-421-188600.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Ronaldo nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00e0n B\u00f2 t\u00f3t</span><br>\r\nRonaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a T\u00e2y Ban Nha 3-3 t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018. CR7 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha-421-188598.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha-421-188598.html\">Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha?</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u0110N vs TBN, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"216","checkdouble":"188610"},{"date":"09:57 16/06","title":"Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi sau c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi TBN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/lap-hattrick-ronaldo-duoc-dong-doi-ca-ngoi-het-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Bernardo Silva kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u00fa hat-trick m\u00e0 Ronaldo v\u1eeba ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca t\u1ee5ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p si\u00eau sao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Fisht Stadium \u0111\u00eam qua. CR7 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap Seleccao gi\u00e0nh gi\u1eadt l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t th\u1ea7n s\u1ea7u h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c De Gea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Si\u00eau sao 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hat-trick trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup. Ronaldo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/lap-hattrick-ronaldo-duoc-dong-doi-ca-ngoi-het-loi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Bernardo Silva \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa anh \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Anh \u1ea5y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00eam qua.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cAnh \u1ea5y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Real Madrid v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Manchester United. Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady trong kho\u1ea3ng 10 n\u0103m qua. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao nh\u01b0 anh \u1ea5y trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o cho anh \u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ghi th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cRonaldo ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n theo tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd gi\u00e0 \u0111i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i, Ronaldo l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo \u1edf Nga\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Silva nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn n\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn Iberia v\u1eeba qua v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i thi nhau d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 3-3 chung cu\u1ed9c. V\u00e0 Bernardo Silva cho r\u1eb1ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Hi\u1ec7p hai th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t l\u1eafm. Nh\u01b0ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Khi anh \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y th\u00ec m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot-421-188600.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Ronaldo nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00e0n B\u00f2 t\u00f3t</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"215","checkdouble":"188611"},{"date":"09:29 16/06","title":"M.U tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n De Gea th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/19/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-146-mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-tu-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m n\u1eefa.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nDe Gea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Real Madrid trong m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ngay sau khi Julen Lopetegui b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Real Madrid bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o David De Gea. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi-180-188491.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson Becker</span> &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a AS Roma \u0111ang chinh chi\u1ebfn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 Real mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 80 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd l\u00e2u, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c M.U v\u00e0 David De Gea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford th\u00eam 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa. Hi\u1ec7n nay v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao De Gea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 350 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m n\u1eefa\" title=\"De Gea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/Edwin-van-der-Sar-phat-bieu-ve-David-de-Gea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m n\u1eefa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. De Gea l\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n trong c\u00fa hattrick c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, trong \u0111\u00f3 b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Man United l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua n\u00e0y. Cristiano \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng, l\u1ebd ra ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a HLV, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu-421-188610.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu-421-188610.html\">Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t 2 n\u0103m t\u00f9</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c, khi ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t La Roja h\u1ed7n mang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o VCK World Cup 2018 ch\u00fat n\u1eefa l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Seleccao \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"214","checkdouble":"188612"},{"date":"07:16 16/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (16/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1662018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size: