21, 221);\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">H\u1ea0NG NH\u00cc ITALIA 2017/18 &ndash; PLAY OFF</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border:1px solid #dddddd;\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">17/06 01:30</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Frosinone - Palermo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"213","checkdouble":"188605"},{"date":"08:13 16/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch (23h ng\u00e0y 16/6): Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf Eriksen","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-peru-vs-dan-mach-23h-ngay-166-khac-biet-o-eriksen.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>S\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch gi\u1eefa s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Peru l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a Christian Eriksen s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 gi\u00fap cho \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u0111\u00eam nay.</h2><h2>Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn sinh t\u1eed</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch (23h ng\u00e0y 166) Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf Eriksen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch (23h ng\u00e0y 166) Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf Eriksen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Peru-vs-Dan-Mach.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bang-c-world-cup-2018-les-bleus-va-phan-con-lai-421-187896.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</span>, Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. M\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out, ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, Peru v\u00e0 Australia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Australia kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u00ec thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu g\u1ecdn h\u01a1n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i tay \u0111\u00f4i gi\u1eefa Peru v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00eam nay s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 theo ch\u00e2n Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1c quan. Trong 15 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Peru gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 10 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 5 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 Uruguay v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Argentina \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ed7i 15 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay. Trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho World Cup, Peru c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Scotland, Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Trong 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u01b0 Chile, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Mexico.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf Eriksen<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Peru v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch th\u1eadt ra c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ngang ng\u1eeda. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn m\u00e1c si\u00eau sao v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Christin Eriksen.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tottenham. Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. S\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u00f9ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 2 con s\u1ed1 \u1edf Premier League l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf Eriksen \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Christian Eriksen dang la niem hy vong lon nhat cua bong da Dan Mach\" title=\"Christian Eriksen \u0111ang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/peru-du-kha-nang-bat-chet-christian-eriksen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Eriksen s\u1ebd mang t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t cho \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Eriksen c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ed3ng g\u00e1nh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch t\u1edbi vinh quang. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3 ch\u1ec9 sau hai &ldquo;m\u00e1y l\u00e0m b\u00e0n&rdquo; Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Robert Lewandowski.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eriksen c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi CH Ireland \u1edf tr\u1eadn play-off l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch t\u1edbi Nga h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Trong v\u00f2ng 2 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Eriksen cho \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c 1 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn (16 b\u00e0n/18 tr\u1eadn).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea5n c\u1ea5n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a &ldquo;nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo; b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 Eriksen t\u1ea1o ra. HLV Age Hareide s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gi\u1eefa Nicolai Jorgensen c\u1ee7a Feyenoord ho\u1eb7c Kasper Dolberg c\u1ee7a Ajax sau khi Bendtner g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy v\u1eady, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Pione Sisto c\u0169ng gi\u00fap cho Eriksen c\u00f3 th\u00eam ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n sau khi l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 t\u1ea1i La Liga trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Celta Vigo. Anh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n s\u1eafc l\u1eb9m c\u1ee7a Eriksen \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00f2n v\u1edbi Peru s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nhau tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Peru t\u1eebng th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup, \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (th\u1eafng 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bulgaria n\u0103m 1970 v\u00e0 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Scotland n\u0103m 1978)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 2 trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam M\u1ef9, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Peru ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n trong 7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Peru kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 46% nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Peru \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110an M\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi trong c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong n\u0103m 2018. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i 444 ph\u00fat kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Nh\u01b0ng \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 l\u1ea7n trong 11 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- C\u1ea3 27 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf World Cup \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Eriksen \u0111\u00e3 ghi 6 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 11 b\u00e0n cho \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Peru vs Dan Mach\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Peru-vs-Dan-Mach-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h4>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</h4>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1: 1-2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"212","checkdouble":"188607"},{"date":"08:51 16/06","title":"H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Ronaldo l\u1eadp h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/huy-diet-tay-ban-nha-ronaldo-lap-them-ky-luc-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha ngay trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf World Cup 2018, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo l\u1eadp h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 s\u00fang \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. V\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, CR7 c\u0169ng \u0111ang li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn n\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn Iberia gi\u1eefa T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00eam qua. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 2 ph\u00fat, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Ronaldo l\u1eadp h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Ronaldo l\u1eadp h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/huy-diet-tay-ban-nha-ronaldo-lap-them-ky-luc-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 <strong>b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nhanh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966</strong>, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Jose Augusto ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf 1 ph\u00fat 35 gi\u00e2y v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Hungary. V\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho Ronaldo m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, <strong>si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong 8 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp,</strong> bao g\u1ed3m World Cup, Euro v\u00e0 Copa America. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 Nam M\u1ef9 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 4 ghi b\u00e0n trong 4 v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup 2006, 2010 v\u00e0 2014. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Ronaldo \u0111\u1ee9ng ngang h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Pele, Uwe Seeler v\u00e0 Miroslav Klose.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty t\u1eeb s\u1edbm, Ronaldo c\u00f2n c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa hat-trick. <strong>Ronaldo c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup (33 tu\u1ed5i 130 ng\u00e0y).</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng B ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 Ma-r\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Iran qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi tay hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Uruguay \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot-421-188600.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Ronaldo nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00e0n B\u00f2 t\u00f3t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha-421-188598.html\">Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"211","checkdouble":"188608"},{"date":"08:20 16/06","title":"Pique b\u1ee9c x\u00fac: \"Ronaldo gi\u1ecfi \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/16/pique-buc-xuc-ronaldo-gioi-an-va-de-kiem-da-phat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ee9c x\u00fac sau khi Cristiano Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick, gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u201cRonaldo c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen qu\u0103ng m\u00ecnh xu\u1ed1ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t\u201d, trung v\u1ec7 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B\u00a0World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00eam qua: \u201cTr\u1eadn n\u00e0y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ba c\u00fa s\u00fat v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 may m\u1eafn c\u1ea3 ba \u0111\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\u201d.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Pique n\u00f3i Ronaldo \u0103n v\u1ea1 tr\u1eadn B\u0110N 3-3 TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Pique n\u00f3i Ronaldo \u0103n v\u1ea1 tr\u1eadn B\u0110N 3-3 TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/a0-9140-1529102593.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pique m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, \u0111\u1ea9y sau gi\u00fap Ronaldo c\u00f3 qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 3-3.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh c\u00e3i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ng\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Real, Nacho \u0111\u01b0a ch\u00e2n ra. Pha va ch\u1ea1m c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 nh\u1eb9 trong c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Ronaldo sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 11m \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, camera c\u00f2n ghi l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Ronaldo nh\u00e1y m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea9n \u00fd v\u1edbi Nacho sau khi ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi ph\u00fat 88, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t ngay s\u00e1t v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m b\u1eb1ng pha kh\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf quay l\u01b0ng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb Gerard Pique \u0111\u1ea9y sau. B\u1eb1ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o, \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng li\u1ec7ng qua h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o \u0111i v\u00e0o g\u00f3c cao, Ronaldo ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t hat-trick c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u00e0 gi\u1eadt l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Seleccao. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \"Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng 2017\" \u1edf ph\u00fat 44 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn. C\u00fa ra ch\u00e2n t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng De Gea l\u1ea1 b\u1eaft kh\u00f4ng d\u00ednh, \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng n\u1ea3y v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi. Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, Pique n\u00f3i: \"\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc m\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a De Gea l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trong khung g\u1ed7\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 kh\u1edfi tranh, T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i Julen Lopetegui v\u00ec \u201c\u0111i \u0111\u00eam\u201d, k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB Real Madrid. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Fernando Hierro \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a l\u00ean thay th\u1ebf d\u00f9 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m HLV. Pique cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y vui v\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\", anh n\u00f3i.\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\u00a0B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha-421-188598.html\">Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-tbn-tiec-nuoi-sau-khi-khong-the-gianh-3-diem-truoc-bdn-421-188599.html\">HLV TBN ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u0110N</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot-421-188600.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Ronaldo nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00e0n B\u00f2 t\u00f3t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-sieu-kich-tinh-421-188601.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lap-hattrick-ronaldo-duoc-hlv-bdn-dua-len-may-421-188603.html\">L\u1eadp hat-trick, Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV B\u0110N \u0111\u01b0a l\u00ean m\u00e2y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-421-188604.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"210","checkdouble":"188609"},{"date":"01:47 16/06","title":"HLV Ma R\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-ma-roc-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-iran.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Herve Renard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran, HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ma R\u1ed1c thua s\u1ed1c 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nMa R\u1ed1c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Iran v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Iran.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Herve Renard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Herve Renard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Herve-Renard-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Ma-Roc-vs-Iran-hinh-anh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Iran v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nTrong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u Iran ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Ma R\u1ed1c mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi 68% v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 13 l\u1ea7n, v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi 32% c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 9 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn Ma R\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aziz Bouhaddouz \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+6 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Herve Renard ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-morocco-vs-iran-tran-dau-bang-b-world-cup-2018-421-188585.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran </span>khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 h\u1ebft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B, b\u1edfi \u1edf nh\u1eefng l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Ma R\u1ed1c th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua Iran</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Herve Renard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran, HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Herve Renard noi ve tran Ma Roc vs Iran\" title=\"HLV Herve Renard n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/hlv-ma-roc-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-iran.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Herve Renard n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, Ma R\u1ed1c c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cTrong kho\u1ea3ng 20 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, Ma R\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u00e9p s\u00e2n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o c\u1ea3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cV\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, TBN v\u00e0 B\u0110N kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng khi c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"209","checkdouble":"188593"},{"date":"02:17 16/06","title":"HLV Iran khen ng\u1ee3i tinh th\u1ea7n qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-iran-khen-ngoi-tinh-than-qua-cam-cua-cac-hoc-tro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Carlos Queiroz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i tinh th\u1ea7n qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c1.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Carlos Queiroz khen ng\u1ee3i c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nIran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u Phi g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ma R\u1ed1c d\u00f9 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Carlos Queiroz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Carlos Queiroz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Carlos-Queiroz-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Ma-Roc-vs-Iran-hinh-anh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Iran \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ma R\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Aziz Bouhaddouz c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn Ma R\u1ed1c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1, qua \u0111\u00f3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Iran v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nCarlos Queiroz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ma-roc-truoc-iran-421-188588.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran</span>, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i tinh th\u1ea7n qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Ma R\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Tuy\u00a0nhi\u00ean, Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nh\u01b0ng tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a Iran \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ma R\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i, song b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Carlos Queiroz tin Iran c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Ma R\u1ed1c, Iran s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo g\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Iran \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Carlos Queiroz noi ve tran Ma Roc vs Iran\" title=\"Carlos Queiroz n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/hlv-iran-khen-ngoi-tinh-than-qua-cam-cua-cac-hoc-tro.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Carlos Queiroz n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Carlos Queiroz kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cHai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi TBN v\u00e0 B\u0110N s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Iran mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"208","checkdouble":"188594"},{"date":"05:09 16/06","title":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a T\u00e2y Ban Nha 3-3 t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018. CR7 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi Nga d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd b\u1ecb gi\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 khi L\u0110B\u0110 TBN quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a T\u00e2y Ban Nha 3-3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a T\u00e2y Ban Nha 3-3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/Ronaldo-lap-hat-trick,-Bo-Dao-Nha-cam-hoa-Tay-Ban-Nha-3-3-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>TBN sa th\u1ea3i Julen Lopetegui ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real sau World Cup 2018, th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a La Roja b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Lopetegui, L\u0110B\u0110 TBN \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ef1u sao Real, Fernando Hierro tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn tinh th\u1ea7n, t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda TBN. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n nh\u01b0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i hay chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a La Roja c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, TBN \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018, La Roja v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN khong he suy yeu boi su ra di cua HLV Lopetegui\" title=\"TBN kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 suy y\u1ebfu b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/tbn.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>TBN kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 suy y\u1ebfu b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf B\u00f2 t\u1ed1t thi \u0111\u1ea5u linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 uy\u1ec3n chuy\u1ec3n. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Iniesta, David Silva, Koke hay Isco, TBN ch\u01a1i bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a B\u0110N.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng (66%) v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m (13 so v\u1edbi 9). La Roja c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 6 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDiego Costa \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung phong h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Nacho c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Patricio.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e3 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi B\u0110N t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, song TBN v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Seleccao kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo lap hat-trick vao luoi Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/044020-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a B\u0110N (15 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o), kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n CR7. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, c\u1ef1u sao M.U l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Seleccao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCR7 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn NHM B\u0110N ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a T\u00e2y Ban Nha 3-3 t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 4. Ronaldo b\u1ecb Nacho, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Real Madrid ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n CR7 b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t. Anh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i De Gea v\u1edbi c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edbi ph\u00fat 44, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David De Gea m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap B\u0110N v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 88, khi B\u0110N \u0111ang b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 3-2 ch\u00ednh Ronaldo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t r\u00e0ng r\u00e0o \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft gi\u00fap Seleccao c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-3,&nbsp;qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi TBN, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 4 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, 3 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c \u1edf World Cup 2018. 3 k\u1ef3 World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, CR7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 68 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ghi 3 b\u00e0n. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 4 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a CR7 \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a B\u0110N \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Ma R\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Iran.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo giup BDN co tran hoa 3-3 truoc TBN\" title=\"Ronaldo gi\u00fap B\u0110N c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/ronaldo-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo gi\u00fap B\u0110N c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn derby b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018, Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Th\u1ebf&nbsp;nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1i d\u1edbp \u0111\u00f3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ecb CR7 x\u00f3a b\u1ecf khi anh l\u1eadp hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRonaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t t\u1eebng l\u1eadp hat-trick trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup (33 tu\u1ed5i 130 ng\u00e0y). Ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 51 hat-trick trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG, 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi TBN c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00fa hat-trick th\u1ee9 51 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha-421-188598.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha-421-188598.html\">Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha?</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u0110N vs TBN, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u00f2n n\u1eefa, c\u1ef1u sao MU l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 4 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ghi b\u00e0n trong 4 k\u1ef3 World Cup li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ghi b\u00e0n trong t\u00e1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede Euro 2016, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap B\u0110N gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Ph\u00e1p. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN, NHM Seleccao \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng CR7 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga gi\u00fap B\u0110N nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so Bo Dao Nha 3-3 Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Thong-so-BDN.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"207","checkdouble":"188595"}]}